source: An entity field containing a dynamic entity reference.
Create a single field to hold references to Users and Nodes. Or Terms and Nodes, or all three.
Display the ID of the referenced entities.
target: Die IDs der referenzierten Entitäten anzeigen.

source: Display the label of the referenced entities.
Display the referenced entities rendered by entity_view().
target: Zeige die referenzierten Entitäten dargestellt durch entity_view().

source: Provides an entity reference field that can reference multiple entity types.
Recursive rendering detected when rendering entity %entity_type: %entity_id, using the %field_name field on the %bundle_name bundle. Aborting rendering.
target: Eine rekursive Darstellung wurde beim Rendern der Entität %entity_type: %entity_id unter Verwendung des Feldes %field_name im Bundle %bundle_name festgestellt. Die Generierung wurde aus diesem Grund abgebrochen.

source: Referenced entity %label does not belong to one of the supported bundles (%bundles).
References to @target_label entities referenced by @field_name @type on @origin_label entities.
Relate each @entity with a @field_name set to the @label.
target: Jede @entity -Entität mit einem @field_name -Feld hat nun einen Bezug zu  @label.

source: Reverse reference from @target_label entities referenced by @field_name @type on @origin_label entities.
Select at least one entity type ID.

The %target_bundle bundle (entity type: %target_entity_type) was deleted. As a result, the %field_name dynamic entity reference field (entity_type: %entity_type, bundle: %bundle) no longer has any valid bundle it can reference. The field is not working correctly anymore and has to be adjusted.
The referenced entity (%type: %id) does not exist.
The referenced entity type (%type) is not allowed for this field.

target: Diese Entität (%type: %id) kann nicht referenziert werden.
Diese Entität (%type: %label) kann nicht referenziert werden.

source: provides a field type/widget/formatter combination for Drupal 8 that allows an entity-reference field to reference more than one entity type.
